    "long_instructions": "## Analyze Data with AI\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to analyze the pizza dataset. The bot will help you summarize key details, identify trends, and suggest how much pizza to order.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nDo This:\r\n1. Upload the **PDF file** of the pizza dataset from the library.\r\n2. Ask AI Chat these questions:\r\n   * Can you summarize this pizza dataset?\r\n   * What trends do you notice?\r\n   * How much pizza should we order based on this data?",
